**Abstract:**
Brief working notes dated June 25, 1991 on the medieval controversy between faith and reason. Discusses how the arrival of Aristotle's major works created an "autonomous understanding of reason" that challenged the historical comprehension of faith, making opposition between faith and Aristotelian reason potentially irreconcilable.

